{
  "stem": "20684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Polish partisans needed doctors, because Polish doctors didn't practice in the forest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So Jewish doctors were the only ones that they could get.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so he got in contact with someone and told him that he was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they didn't believe him at first, and said, well, you know, take me, and take my wife, and-- so the condition was that if he can't prove that he's a doctor, when-- when they'll take him to the partisans, the three of us will be shot.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, people told him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it was-- it was a known fact.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's like, you know, like people give you a tip.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A horse will win something, or you know, bet-- put your money on that horse to win the Melbourne Cup.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or, you know, things like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They tell you, look, you know, because they find out that he was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was helping.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Doctors help people in the-- in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, they knew he was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they said that, you know, they need doctors in the partisans, and we might-- we'll that you can get smuggled out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got smuggled out by-- by similar guards, Ukrainian guards, in a cart, drawn cart with clothing, with lots of clothing in a pile of clothing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we're put underneath the clothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were taken out through the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Guards were searching it, and I remember they were prodding with fork.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was all arranged in such a way that they wouldn't hit us, because it was-- everybody was on the take, on those-- the-- the Ukrainian guards knew that there were people being smuggled out for some reason, for money.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it was not money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was essential services.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
